			<div class="grid_8"><h1>Indulge in Luxury - Reunite with Nature</h1></div><div class="richtext grid_8">
<a name="t"></a>
<p>There is a place which is veiled in the peaceful aura of the silent highland and the silky scent of its wild flowers and plants. There is a place with small paths that wind around pine-sprangled hills like the mysterious sound of the spring that comes along with the breath of the wind. There is a place where the luminescence of the dew embraces the first rays of dawn and yield a play of colors so fascinating that one wants to stay up all night to be its witness. Dalat Edensee is the place where time and space surge, and where life resumes its primary meaning.</p>
<p>Discreetly hidden at the waterfront of Tuyen Lam Lake, Dalat Edensee perfectly unifies the ‘Rheingauer’ way of life with Tuyen Lam’s botanical wonders. Be amazed by the charm of the fascinating nature surrounding the resort. Revive when you feel the breeze that whispers through the pine forest. Relax your mind and spirit while wandering around a marvel of architecture - a palace that directly adjoins to the nature and seems to have no limits except for the indefinite contours of the distance.</p>
<p> </p>
